space.serialization

Class MyJsonList

  • java.lang.Object
    • space.serialization.MyJsonList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<org.json.simple.JSONObject>

    public class MyJsonList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<org.json.simple.JSONObject>
    Represents a MyJsonList for classes and entities in the game this is a wrapper class for the raw JSONArray from the library It enables type safety rather than being generic - to avoid accidently put the wrong data type
    Author:
    Shweta Barapatre
